formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	It is the responsibility of management to prepare the financial statement of firm. The firm has prepared financial statement by following the mercantile method of accounting. The promoter has passed all necessary entries in accounts and reported all bank accounts in the financial statements and based on the unaudited accounts produced before us for given this certificate and relied on same for reporting to RERA Authority while certifying Form 3.
2.	The compilation & certification of figures in the said RERA Form - 3 along-with applicable annexure are based & relied on ?  
Latest Architect?s & Engineer?s certificates regarding estimated construction cost, Nos. of Garage/covered/Open parking as per RERA, Calculation of carpet area of each & every units of the said project as per RERA & Percentage of completion of on-site works, 
-	Duly signed plan passed, 
-	Previous years Audited financials, 
-	Duly certified provisional financials up to (30/04/2022), 
-	Duly certified secured and unsecured loans, estimated project cost & receivables from the allottee by the management of entity and; 
-	such other information & explanations provided by the entity & proprietor/partner/director of the Entity, 
which, to the best of our knowledge and belief were necessary for the purpose of issuing this certificate.
3.	Amount deposited and withdrawn from the bank account reflects only booking receipts collected and utilized in the project.
4.	We clarify that physical copy of Form No.3 & 3A contains certain explanatory and other notes to the various clauses which do not find place in the electronic Form No. 3 & 3A. In view of this, the electronic Form No.3 & 3A should be read together with all the notes appearing in the physical Form No.3 & 3A and in case of any conflict, the information and details provided in physical copy shall prevail.
5.	Management of the entity has provided Customer ID, details of PAN / Aadhar Card, and Mobile Numbers of the allottees, Date of Registered Agreement for sale and Encumbrance Status and we have relied on the same while giving this certificate.

6.	As per information and explanation received from the promoter, Flat No: 1304 in C Building, is not given at the time of online application and hence system is not accepting this flat detail. The promoter has already sent on 29.11.2019 to the RERA department mail address and submitted affidavit in this matter for addition of this flat but till date it is not updated in the Form 3A sheet hence unable to update in the sheet.
7.	As per Information and explanation received from the promoter has directly executed Sale deed to the allotees without entering registered agreement for sale hence, in Column or detail of Date of Agreement for sale, we have entered sale deed for reporting purpose. 
8.	The Promoter has repaid secured loan taken from Capri Gold Capital Limited and hence In Encumbrance Status, we have given released as there is no dues / outstanding of secured loan while giving this certificate. The promoter has not produced NOC taken from the bank while giving this certificate.
9. The promoter has not produced any NOC taken from the bank hence based on the detail given by the promoter we have filled the detail however, promoter has repaid all the loan taken from the bank hence now there is no NOC required from the bank
